data.description:
New updated price! Your search for a country oasis ends here! Nestled on over 7 acres in the hills and trees southwest of Abilene, this home boasts privacy and attentive updates for you to enjoy immediately! With the intention of being here a long time, the sellers have lovingly replaced windows, the HVAC, the roof, the back porch steps, and updated plumbing to pex. They have added auxiliary heat, a pergola, a turfed area, and a refreshing hard-sided above-ground pool. They have even updated the chicken coop! Their plans have changed, and this home is now ready for you! 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, granite countertops, semi-open floorplan with vaulted ceilings and fantastic natural lighting. Too many small and large updates to list! Come see if this is your place! 20x30 detached shop with electricity. 12x20 storage building stays.
Buyer to verify schools as it is near the line between Merkel ISD and Jim Ned ISD.
